{"tid":326509,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【離奇命案】廢老打麻將猝死  街坊：連續開扛後 激動暴斃","createTime":"2017-07-18T05:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T06:19:18.000Z","uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b14b239b31c4bea1d819f1f34515dc24365ff9a4","tid":326509,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170718/large/1500339830_cc1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170718%2Flarge%2F1500339830_cc1a.jpg&h=30ae3ece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打麻將應持平常心，不然太激動，分分鐘喪命。四川自貢昨日下午發生一宗悲劇，富順縣一麻將館內，一名年約50歲的男子在打麻將時突然暈厥倒地，醫護人員到場搶救，仍返魂乏術。<br />\n<br />\n對於男子的死因，當地居民說法不一，有指男子本身患有高血壓，當時取得一手好牌，連續多次開杠，激動後猝死；甚至有居民懷疑他是中毒身亡。當局對男子死亡的原因，仍在調查中。"},{"pid":"f57637385c365ada80563d36949eb82340d3aa18","tid":326509,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:35:34.000Z","msg":"雀聖4之自摸扞上扞"},{"pid":"6ce3efe491c15015405c0150a3e8f8bd9d307c81","tid":326509,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8023139e93158ce811ab1a78ad1b62044ce183b","tid":326509,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:19:18.000Z","msg":"防止老人痴呆嘛"}]}